    "title_en": "Large sets of mutually orthogonal quantum Latin squares",
    "abstract_en": "How large can a set of mutually orthogonal quantum Latin squares (MOQLS) get? We show that a set of n - 2 MOQLS of order n is necessarily classical and construct large non-classical sets of MOQLS of orders that are prime powers, improving both the previously known lower and upper bounds.",
